snippet.title: Wacky Wheels
snippet.description:
This is Wacky Wheels, an arcade racing game released by Apogee in 1994. It was fun, especially the multiplayer mode against friends :)

If you want to know history on the development and why it is related to another game, Skunny Kart, check out my other video:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j0JzpjINeE0
